data.description: Have you been looking for a large, affordable home in the South Jefferson School District? We welcome you to 24 Prospect St in the village of Adams, which is just a minute or two from Interstate 81 and the South Jefferson Middle/High School. At 2,328 square feet, this 5 bed 2 bath home is impressively spacious and has incredible curb appeal. The sun room leads out to the back deck which overlooks the shady back yard, a relaxing pool, and also provides access to the hot tub and the 2 stall detached garage. With this kind of size, there are endless options to make it your own. Schedule a showing today to see how this stately home can be the one for you!
